{
  "stem": "15197.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But these were children 10, 11, 12, 13, 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were the smugglers bringing in some food into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were small.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And through all kinds of holes, through all kinds of places where they were able and they knew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went out, they bought something, brought in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Many smugglers were killed at the ghetto wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Little smugglers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were poems, smuggler poems, which writers in the ghetto wrote about the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I say-- I said before that I was smuggling in dynamite.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went back into the ghetto and I went back to the place where it was the center of the illegal youth leadership.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was also the place where a primitive ammunition factory of the fighters organization was organized.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And over there I met the leadership.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Quite often I was, always just a smuggler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Always every smuggler it was dangerous to go over the wall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And over there I remember when they showed me how they are preparing the so-called Molotov cocktail bottles, which later on it played quite a role during the uprising in the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went back, yes, quite a few times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In this specific place I met Anielewicz, [INAUDIBLE] Anielewicz, who was the leader of the uprising in the Warsaw ghetto, and I met the other people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not a question about going every day or every other day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the assignment was-- when I have-- it could have been once a week, once in two weeks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When it got closer to the uprising, it was more often because it was-- the [INAUDIBLE], the people knew that deportation, that the Warsaw ghetto was going to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
